org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.adapter

Interface WritableDataAdapter<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of entries that this adapter works on.
    All Superinterfaces:
    DataAdapter<T>, DataReader<Object>, DataWriter<T,Object>, Persistable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    GeotoolsFeatureDataAdapter, IndexDependentDataAdapter<T>, InternalDataAdapter<T>, RowMergingDataAdapter<T,M>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDataAdapter, AvroFeatureDataAdapter, DistortionGroupManagement.DistortionDataAdapter, FeatureDataAdapter, ImageChipDataAdapter, InternalDataAdapterWrapper, RasterDataAdapter

    public interface WritableDataAdapter<T>
extends DataAdapter<T>, DataWriter<T,Object>
    This extends the basic DataAdapter interface to be able to ingest data in addition to query for it. Any data adapter used for ingest should implement this interface.
